title: LEARNIT X BOBBLE AI – DATATHON & INTERACTIVE SESSIONS
description: In collaboration with the School of Information Security and Data Science (SISDS), LearnIT Club successfully hosted a dynamic two-day event with Bobble AI. Held on September 9–10, 2024, it featured hands-on learning, industry expert talks, and a thrilling Datathon, offering students deep insights into data, innovation, and career readiness.
